claim.claim-text:
14. A blank for folding into an antiskid dunnage, the blank comprising:
a honeycomb panel having a first and second opposed faces, and having a V-groove in the first face between two adjacent panel sections;
a single antiskid cohesive including a first portion applied as a single layer on the V-groove and a second portion applied as a single layer on a substantial portion of at least one of the two adjacent panels, on the first face thereof;
wherein the blank can be folded along the V-groove into a dunnage configuration, and thence be automatically maintained in the dunnage configuration by activation of the first portion of antiskid cohesive, wherein the second portion of the single antiskid cohesive is exposed to a work surface and provides antiskid thereagainst which is higher than without the single antiskid cohesive.
